OL,7,FIn May 2023, ITV announced it had
OL,8,Finstructed Jane Mulcahy KC to carry
OL,9,Fout an external review following the
OL,10,Fdeparture of Phillip Schofield from
OL,11,FThis Morning after 20 years on the
OL,12,Fshow. Days after leaving, Schofield
OL,13,Fadmitted to lying about an "unwise,
OL,14,Fbut not illegal" affair he had with a
OL,15,Fyounger colleague on the show.
OL,17,FThe announcement prompted a public
OL,18,Fconversation about the power dynamic
OL,19,Fbetween on-screen personalities and
OL,20,Fmore junior members of staff within
OL,21,Fthe television industry.
